title: Hurricane Joaquin to miss US, forecast strongly suggests
text:
Hurricane Joaquin to miss US, forecast strongly suggests 
Published By: News-press.com - Today 
The forecast models continue to indicate a track offshore of the United States east coast from the Carolinas to the mid-Atlantic states.
